product.description:
Description

Buying a new hair dryer because the nozzle is broken or missing is not worth it. You may need such a practical and convenient blow dryer comb. The replacement hair dryer nozzle comb is made from premium material, which can output the wind stably for your convenience. Help to cleanse your hair, leaving hair beautifully radiant, sleek and shiny as you style.

Features

-Color:Black
-Material:Plastic
-Size:13.00X5.00X5.00cm/5.11X1.97X1.97in
-Made from premium and sturdy materials, this hair dryer nozzle attachment is very durable and safe to use.
-Good workmanship, the blow dryer attachment is not easy to deform and break, for you to use rest assured.
-Evenly and gently diffuse hair to maximize volume while eliminating curling, bring you much convenience.
-By gathering and dispersing wind through the nozzle, you can quickly dry your hair and reduce impact for your hair.
-Compact in size, light in weight, this comb attachment for hair blow dryer is easy to install, save your time and efforts.
